      "@id": "/how-to-avoid-african-grey-parrot-scams/#faq",
      "mainEntity": [
        {"@type":"Question","name":"How do I know if an African Grey parrot listing is a scam?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Key red flags: pricing below $1,500 (Congo) or $1,200 (Timneh), seller only accepting Zelle/CashApp/Western Union/wire transfer, photos that appear on multiple sites, no CITES Appendix I documentation offered, breeder website created less than 6 months ago, and refusal to do a live video call showing the actual bird."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What is the USDA AWA license and how do I verify it?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The USDA AWA (Animal Welfare Act) Class A license is required for all professional bird breeders in the United States. Verify any breeder's license at aphis.usda.gov/awa/public-search — enter the breeder's name, state, or license number."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What is CITES Appendix I and why does it matter for African Grey parrots?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"CITES Appendix I lists African Grey parrots as a protected species. All captive-bred African Greys sold in the US must have CITES Appendix I documentation proving captive-bred status. Any seller who cannot provide this is selling an illegally obtained bird or running a scam."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What is a safe payment method for buying an African Grey parrot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Safe: credit cards (reversible via chargeback) and PayPal Goods & Services (buyer protection). Never use Zelle, CashApp, Venmo, Western Union, MoneyGram, wire transfer, or gift cards — these are untraceable and non-reversible."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What should I do if I was scammed buying a parrot online?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Report immediately to: (1) FBI IC3 at ic3.gov; (2) FTC at reportfraud.ftc.gov; (3) BBB Scam Tracker at bbb.org/scamtracker; (4) Your state Attorney General; (5) Your bank or credit card company to initiate a chargeback."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"How much should an African Grey parrot cost?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Legitimate captive-bred CITES-documented Congo African Greys cost $1,500–$3,500. Timneh African Greys cost $1,200–$2,500. Any listing below $800 is almost certainly a scam."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"Are parrot eggs for sale legitimate?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. 'African Grey parrot eggs for sale' listings are virtually always scams. Hatching requires specialized incubation, 24/7 monitoring, and formula feeding every 2 hours for 12+ weeks. No legitimate seller ships unhatched parrot eggs."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"How do I reverse image search a parrot photo?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Right-click any parrot photo and select 'Search image' (Chrome) or upload to images.google.com or tineye.com. If the same photo appears on multiple sites or unrelated listings, the images are stolen. 92% of scam sites use stolen photos."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What documents should come with a legitimate captive-bred African Grey?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A legitimate captive-bred African Grey should come with: (1) CITES Appendix I captive-bred documentation; (2) Hatch certificate with band/ring number; (3) DNA sexing certificate; (4) Avian veterinarian health certificate; (5) USDA AWA license number of the breeding facility."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"Is C.A.Gs a legitimate African Grey breeder?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. C.A.Gs (Congo African Greys), owned by Mark and Teri Benjamin, is a USDA AWA licensed captive-bred African Grey parrot breeder in Midland, Texas. All birds are CITES Appendix I documented, DNA sexed, and avian vet certified. Verify the USDA AWA license at aphis.usda.gov/awa/public-search."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"What is the advance-fee fraud scam for parrots?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The scammer posts a bird at an attractive price, takes a deposit, then invents escalating fees — 'shipping insurance,' 'CITES customs fee,' 'thermal crate.' Each payment is followed by another fee. The bird never exists. Victims lose $200–$2,000+ before the scammer disappears."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"How do I check how old a breeder's website is?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Use a WHOIS lookup at whois.domaintools.com or lookup.icann.org. Enter the breeder's domain and look for the Creation Date. Any breeder website created less than 6 months ago claiming years of experience is a major red flag."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"Does C.A.Gs screen its African Greys for PBFD and Polyomavirus?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Every C.A.Gs chick is screened for PBFD (Psittacine Beak and Feather Disease) and Avian Polyomavirus (APV), PCR DNA sexed, and examined by a board-certified avian veterinarian before leaving Midland, TX. Each bird ships with its hatch certificate, closed band, and a 72-hour written health guarantee. A scammer cannot produce any of this paperwork, because there is no bird behind it."}},
        {"@type":"Question","name":"How much does shipping cost from a legitimate African Grey breeder?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"From C.A.Gs, shipping is quoted upfront and never changes after payment: $185 for airport pickup (IATA-compliant live-animal cargo on Delta, United, or American) or $350 for home delivery. The scam pattern is the opposite — a fake transport company invents escalating invoices after you have already paid. If the shipping cost was not fixed in writing before your deposit, you are not dealing with a legitimate breeder."}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
`;
---

<BaseLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical={canonical}
  ogType="article"
  schemaJson={schemaJson}
  extraHeadHtml={extraHeadHtml}
  hideGlobalCta
>

<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){html{scroll-behavior:auto}}
body{font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#1c1a18;background:#fff}
:root{--green:#2D6A4F;--clay:#e8604c;--clay-ink:#c8472f;--clay-text:#b04228;--peach:#ffd6cf;--mint:#c2f7d4;--cream:#faf7f4;--dark:#1c1a18;--muted:#6b6560;--border:#ede5dc;--max-w:1140px}
img{max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block}
a{color:var(--green);text-decoration:none}
a:hover{color:var(--clay)}
p{margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75}
h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;line-height:1.25;color:var(--dark)}
h2{font-size:clamp(1.3rem,3.4vw,1.65rem);margin:2rem 0 .75rem;color:var(--green)}
h3{font-size:clamp(1.05rem,2.2vw,1.2rem);margin:1.5rem 0 .5rem}
h5{font-size:1rem;margin:1.25rem 0 .4rem;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;color:var(--muted)}
h6,.qa-label{font-size:.875rem;margin:1rem 0 .35rem;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.callout-green h5{color:var(--green);margin:0 0 8px;font-size:.95rem;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif}
.trust-card h3,.trust-card h5{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--green);margin:0 0 6px;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-weight:700}
ul,ol{padding-left:1.4rem;margin-bottom:1rem}
li{margin-bottom:.4rem;line-height:1.7}
.container{max-width:var(--max-w);margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
/* ===== INFOGRAPHIC: 6 SIGNS OF A LEGITIMATE BREEDER ===== */
.ig-legit{margin:2rem auto;max-width:760px;background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 26px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(45,106,79,.35);display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:400px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
.ig-legit-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-legit-eyebrow{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--peach);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
.ig-legit-title{display:block;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.25;margin-top:4px;color:#fff}
.ig-legit-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);grid-auto-rows:1fr;gap:12px;flex:1;min-height:0}
.ig-legit-card{background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.ig-legit-card svg{color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-legit-card strong{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.25;color:#fff}
.ig-legit-card span{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.45}
@media(max-width:640px){
  .ig-legit{height:auto;padding:20px 18px}
  .ig-legit-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-auto-rows:auto}
  .ig-legit-title{font-size:18px}
}
@media(max-width:420px){.ig-legit-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
/* ===== SHARED INFOGRAPHIC PANEL — same standard as .ig-legit (760px / 400px desktop, auto mobile) ===== */
.ig-panel{margin:2rem auto;max-width:760px;background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 26px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(45,106,79,.35);display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:400px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
.ig-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-eyebrow{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--peach);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
.ig-title{display:block;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.25;margin-top:4px;color:#fff}
.ig-body{flex:1;min-height:0;display:grid;gap:12px}
.ig-foot{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);text-align:center;line-height:1.45}
.ig-cols-2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-auto-rows:1fr}
.ig-cols-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);grid-auto-rows:1fr}
.ig-cols-5{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);grid-auto-rows:1fr}
.ig-card{background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.ig-card svg{color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-card strong{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.25;color:#fff}
.ig-card span{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.45}
.ig-card.center{text-align:center;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-start}
.ig-card.bad{background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);border-color:rgba(232,96,76,.45)}
.ig-card.bad strong{color:var(--peach)}
.ig-card.bad svg{color:var(--peach)}
/* red-flag pills */
.ig-flag{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:rgba(232,96,76,.16);border:1px solid rgba(232,96,76,.28);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 14px}
.ig-flag .x{color:var(--peach);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}
.ig-flag span{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.35}
/* check rows (CITES checklist) */
.ig-check{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;background:rgba(82,194,122,.14);border:1px solid rgba(82,194,122,.22);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px}
.ig-check .mk{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--mint);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1.3}
.ig-check div strong{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:2px}
.ig-check div span{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.4}
.ig-check.bad{background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);border-color:rgba(232,96,76,.45)}
.ig-check.bad .mk{color:var(--peach)}
.ig-check.bad div strong{color:var(--peach)}
/* 3-step process with arrows */
.ig-steps{grid-template-columns:1fr 26px 1fr 26px 1fr;align-items:stretch;gap:0}
.ig-step{background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 14px;text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px}
.ig-step svg{color:#fff}
.ig-step .lbl{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--peach);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em}
.ig-step strong{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.3}
.ig-step span{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.45}
.ig-arrow{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--peach);font-size:20px;font-weight:700}
/* escalation ladder rows */
.ig-rows{grid-auto-rows:1fr;gap:10px}
.ig-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 16px;border-left:4px solid rgba(232,96,76,.6)}
.ig-row .stg{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}
.ig-row strong{display:block;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.3}
.ig-row em{display:block;font-style:normal;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.35}
.ig-row .amt{font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:var(--peach);white-space:nowrap}
.ig-row.gain{border-left-color:rgba(82,194,122,.7)}
.ig-row.gain .amt{color:var(--mint)}
.ig-row.final{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-left-color:#e8604c}
.ig-row.final strong{color:var(--peach)}
/* real-vs-fake columns */
.ig-vs-col{background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;border:1px solid rgba(82,194,122,.3)}
.ig-vs-col.bad{border-color:rgba(232,96,76,.45)}
.ig-vs-col .vs-head{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;text-align:center;color:var(--mint);margin-bottom:4px}
.ig-vs-col.bad .vs-head{color:var(--peach)}
.ig-vs-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;flex:1}
.ig-vs-item .mk{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--mint);flex-shrink:0}
.ig-vs-col.bad .ig-vs-item .mk{color:var(--peach)}
.ig-vs-item span{font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);line-height:1.35}
/* surge chart columns */
.ig-chart-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:0}
.ig-chart-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.ig-bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:9px}
.ig-bar-row .yr{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-size:12px;width:36px;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-bar-row .bar{background:#e8604c;height:12px;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0}
.ig-bar-row .pct{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap}
.ig-pbar{margin-bottom:11px}
.ig-pbar .pb-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:4px}
.ig-pbar .pb-top .nm{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
.ig-pbar .pb-top .vl{color:var(--peach);font-weight:700}
.ig-pbar .pb-track{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);height:7px;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.ig-pbar .pb-track .pb-fill{background:#e8604c;height:100%}
@media(max-width:640px){
  .ig-panel{height:auto;padding:20px 18px}
  .ig-title{font-size:18px}
  .ig-cols-3,.ig-cols-5{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-auto-rows:auto}
  .ig-cols-2{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-auto-rows:auto}
  .ig-steps{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .ig-arrow{transform:rotate(90deg);padding:6px 0}
  .ig-row{grid-template-columns:60px 1fr auto;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px}
}
@media(max-width:420px){.ig-cols-3,.ig-cols-5{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
/* ===== BREADCRUMB ===== */

/* ===== HERO ===== */
#hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#162f23 0%,#1f4d38 45%,#2d6a4f 100%);padding:56px 0 52px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
#hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-80px;right:-80px;width:400px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(232,96,76,.12) 0%,transparent 65%);pointer-events:none}
.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 420px;gap:48px;align-items:center}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(232,96,76,.18);border:1px solid rgba(232,96,76,.35);color:#ffccc5;border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.8px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:20px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
.hero-h1{font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.55rem);font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:16px}
.hero-sub{font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);max-width:600px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px}
.hero-snippet{background:rgba(255,255,255,.09);border-left:3px solid var(--clay);padding:14px 18px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin-bottom:28px;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.88);line-height:1.6}
.hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:24px}
.btn-primary{background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(232,96,76,.4);transition:background .2s,transform .15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#b03c26;transform:translateY(-2px);color:#fff}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:#fff;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);transition:all .2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:#fff}
.hero-trust{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-trust-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-size:12.5px}
.hero-trust-dot{width:8px;height:8px;background:#52c27a;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}

/* Hero infographic panel */
.hero-infographic{height:350px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(60,30,10,.3)}
@media(max-width:900px){.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.hero-infographic{display:flex;height:auto;min-height:300px;max-height:350px;width:100%;margin-top:20px}}

/* ===== COUNTER SNIPPETS ===== */
#counters{background:#fff;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(60,30,10,.04)}
.counters-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
.counter-item{padding:20px 20px;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.counter-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.counter-num{font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);display:block;line-height:1.1}
.counter-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;margin-top:5px;display:block;line-height:1.3}
@media(max-width:640px){.counters-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.counter-item:nth-child(2){border-right:none}.counter-item:nth-child(3),.counter-item:nth-child(4){border-top:1px solid var(--border)}.counter-item:nth-child(4){border-right:none}}

/* ===== CONTENT BODY ===== */
.main-section{padding:36px 0}
.content-body{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto}
.content-body a:not(.btn-primary):not(.btn-outline):not(.btn-primary-pill):not(.section-next-link){text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px}
.content-body a:not(.btn-primary):not(.btn-outline):not(.btn-primary-pill):not(.section-next-link):hover{text-decoration:none}

/* Key takeaways */
.takeaways-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f9f4,#e6f5ee);border:1px solid #b7dfc7;border-radius:16px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:32px}
.takeaways-box h2{color:var(--green);margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:1.25rem}
.takeaways-box ul{list-style:none;padding:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:9px}
.takeaways-box li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:9px;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.55}
.takeaways-box li::before{content:'✓';color:var(--green);font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
@media(max-width:580px){.takeaways-box ul{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

/* TOC */
.toc-box{background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:40px}
.toc-box h2{font-size:1rem;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:14px;color:var(--dark);font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.toc-list{list-style:none;padding:0;columns:2;column-gap:28px}
.toc-list li{break-inside:avoid;margin-bottom:7px;font-size:13.5px}
.toc-list a{color:var(--green);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:7px}
.toc-list a span.num{color:#b83c26;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;min-width:18px}
.toc-list a:hover{color:var(--clay)}
@media(max-width:600px){.toc-list{columns:1}}

/* Section content */
.section-block{padding:40px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.section-block:last-child{border-bottom:none}
/* Sticky header is ~96px tall — keep jumped-to headings visible below it */
.section-block,.inquiry-section,.form-section,#hero,#counters,#faq{scroll-margin-top:110px}

/* Snippet paragraph */
.snippet-answer{background:#f0f9f4;border-left:4px solid var(--green);padding:16px 20px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin:18px 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7}

/* Warning box */
.warn-box{background:#fff8f6;border:1px solid #f4beb5;border-radius:10px;padding:18px 22px;margin:20px 0;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start}
.warn-icon{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1.4}
.warn-body strong{display:block;margin-bottom:4px;color:#b83c26;font-size:14px}
.warn-body p,.warn-body{font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a2018;margin:0}

/* Stat callout */
.stat-callout{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:22px 26px;margin:24px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}
.stat-callout .stat-num{font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;color:#7ce8a6;flex-shrink:0}
.stat-callout p{margin:0;font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,.88)}

/* Scam type cards */
.scam-types-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin:22px 0}
.scam-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;border-top:3px solid var(--clay);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(60,30,10,.04)}
.scam-card h3{margin-top:0;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--dark)}
.scam-card p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:0;line-height:1.55}
@media(max-width:580px){.scam-types-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

/* Image placeholder */
.img-placeholder{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f4f2,#e8ede9);border:2px dashed #a8c9b8;border-radius:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:24px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;margin:24px 0;gap:8px}
.img-placeholder .ph-icon{font-size:28px;opacity:.5}
.img-placeholder .ph-label{font-weight:600;color:var(--green);font-size:13px}
.img-placeholder .ph-size{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}

/* Red flag cards */
.red-flag-item{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px 28px;margin:18px 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:56px 1fr;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(60,30,10,.05);transition:box-shadow .2s}
.red-flag-item:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(60,30,10,.1)}
.rf-number{width:48px;height:48px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c94d3a,var(--clay));border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.rf-content h3{margin-top:0;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--dark)}
.rf-content p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.6}
.rf-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:#fff0ee;border:1px solid #f4c4bc;border-radius:50px;padding:4px 10px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#b83c26}

/* Verification steps */
.verify-steps{counter-reset:verify-step;margin:20px 0}
.verify-step{display:grid;grid-template-columns:44px 1fr;gap:16px;padding:20px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);counter-increment:verify-step}
.verify-step:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.step-num{width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.step-content h3,.step-content h4{margin-top:0;margin-bottom:5px;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--dark)}
.step-content p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.6}
.step-content a{color:var(--green);font-weight:600;word-break:break-all}
.step-content a:hover{color:var(--clay)}

/* Inquiry form */
.inquiry-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#162f23,var(--green));border-radius:16px;padding:36px;text-align:center;margin:40px 0}
.inquiry-section h2{color:#fff;margin-top:0;font-size:1.4rem}
.inquiry-section > p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin-bottom:22px;font-size:14.5px}
.inq-form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;max-width:540px;margin:0 auto;text-align:left}
.inq-form-grid input,.inq-form-grid textarea,.inq-form-grid select{width:100%;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:9px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);background:rgba(255,255,255,.09);color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;outline:none}
.inq-form-grid input::placeholder,.inq-form-grid textarea::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.inq-form-grid input:focus,.inq-form-grid textarea:focus{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);background:rgba(255,255,255,.14)}
.inq-full{grid-column:1/-1}
.inq-submit{background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;border:none;padding:14px;border-radius:50px;font-size:14.5px;font-weight:700;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;cursor:pointer;width:100%;margin-top:6px;transition:background .2s}
.inq-submit:hover{background:#b03c26}
.inq-note{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);margin-top:10px;text-align:center}

/* ===== QUESTIONS GRID (Section 11) ===== */
.questions-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin:24px 0}
.q-item{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:20px 22px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(60,30,10,.04);transition:box-shadow .2s}
.q-item:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(60,30,10,.09)}
.q-num{width:42px;height:42px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),#3d8c68);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;letter-spacing:-.5px}
.q-body h3{margin-top:0;margin-bottom:5px;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--dark)}
.q-body p{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.6}
@media(max-width:680px){.questions-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

.cta-inline{background:#f0f9f4;border:1px solid #b7dfc7;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta-inline p{margin:0;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--dark);flex:1}
.nl-mid{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#162f23,#1f4d38);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 28px;margin:32px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.nl-mid-text .nl-eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#ffb3a6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;margin-bottom:6px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
.nl-mid-text h4{font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin:0 0 4px}
.nl-mid-text p{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);margin:0}
.nl-mid-form{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;min-width:260px}
.nl-mid-form input[type="email"]{flex:1;min-width:180px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:#fff;font-size:13.5px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;outline:none}
.nl-mid-form input[type="email"]::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.nl-mid-form input[type="email"]:focus{border-color:var(--clay)}
.nl-mid-form button{background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;border:none;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .2s}
.nl-mid-form button:hover{background:#b03c26}
.btn-primary-pill{background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:700;font-size:13.5px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(232,96,76,.35);transition:background .2s,transform .15s;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block}
.btn-primary-pill:hover{background:#b03c26;transform:translateY(-1px);color:#fff}

/* ===== FULL FORM SECTION (Section 12) ===== */
.form-section{margin:40px 0}
.form-inner{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(60,30,10,.07)}
.form-header-green{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#162f23,var(--green));padding:30px 36px;text-align:center}
.form-header-green h2{color:#fff;margin:0 0 8px;font-size:1.45rem}
.form-header-green p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
.form-icon{font-size:28px;display:block;margin-bottom:10px}
.cag-form{padding:28px 36px}
.form-row-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
.form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;margin-bottom:14px}
.form-group label{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--dark)}
.req{color:var(--clay)}
.form-group input,.form-group select,.form-group textarea{padding:11px 14px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;font-size:14px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;color:var(--dark);background:#fff9f6;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s}
.form-group input:focus,.form-group select:focus,.form-group textarea:focus{border-color:var(--clay);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(232,96,76,.1);background:#fff}
.form-group textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:100px}
.btn-submit-full{width:100%;background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;border:none;padding:14px;border-radius:50px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(232,96,76,.38);transition:background .2s,transform .15s}
.btn-submit-full:hover{background:#b03c26;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.form-trust-pills{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;padding:16px 36px 24px;justify-content:center}
.form-trust-pills span{background:#eaf4ef;color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(45,106,79,.2);border-radius:50px;padding:5px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
@media(max-width:600px){.form-row-2{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cag-form{padding:20px 20px}.form-header-green{padding:24px 20px}.form-trust-pills{padding:14px 20px 18px}}

/* ===== STORY BLOCK + CASE STUDIES (Sections 13–15) ===== */
.story-block h3{color:var(--green);font-size:1.05rem;margin:1.75rem 0 .5rem}
.story-block h3:first-child{margin-top:.5rem}

.story-case{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(60,30,10,.05)}
.case-header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff8f6,#fff0ee);border-bottom:1px solid #f4c4bc;padding:18px 24px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.case-badge{background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;border-radius:50px;padding:4px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;flex-shrink:0}
.case-header h3{margin:0;font-size:1rem;color:var(--dark);flex:1;min-width:200px}
.case-state{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif}
.case-body{padding:20px 24px}
.case-body p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted)}
.case-body em{color:var(--dark);font-style:italic}
.case-body strong{color:var(--dark)}
.case-lesson{background:#fff8f6;border:1px solid #f4c4bc;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;color:#7a2d1f}

.callout-green{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f9f4,#e6f5ee);border:1px solid #b7dfc7;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0}
.callout-green h4{color:var(--green);margin:0 0 8px;font-size:.95rem;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif}
.callout-green p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.65}
.callout-green a{color:var(--green);font-weight:600}
.callout-green a:hover{color:var(--clay)}

/* ===== SECTION JUMP NAV ===== */
:global(.section-next-nav){text-align:right;padding-top:18px;margin-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #ede5dc}
:global(.section-next-link){display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:#2D6A4F;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;transition:color .2s,gap .15s;padding:10px 0 10px 12px;margin:-10px 0}
:global(.section-next-link:hover){color:#b04228;gap:10px}

/* ===== PAYMENT TABLE ===== */
.payment-table-wrap{overflow-x:auto;margin:20px 0;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(60,30,10,.05)}
.payment-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px}
.payment-table thead tr{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.payment-table thead th{padding:12px 16px;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-align:left;white-space:nowrap}
.payment-table tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.payment-table tbody tr:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.payment-table tbody tr:nth-child(even){background:#faf7f4}
.payment-table td{padding:11px 16px;line-height:1.5;vertical-align:top;color:var(--muted)}
.payment-table td:first-child{font-weight:600;color:var(--dark)}
.td-safe{color:#2d6a4f;font-weight:700}
.td-unsafe{color:#b83c26;font-weight:700}
.td-caution{color:#8a6800;font-weight:700}

/* ===== DOCUMENTATION CHECKLIST ===== */
.doc-checklist{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:20px 0}
.doc-checklist li{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.doc-checklist li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.doc-check-icon{width:28px;height:28px;background:#eaf4ef;border:1px solid #b7dfc7;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.doc-check-body strong{display:block;font-size:14px;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:3px}
.doc-check-body p{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.55}

/* ===== TRUST SIGNAL CARDS ===== */
.trust-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin:20px 0}
.trust-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(60,30,10,.04)}
.trust-card-icon{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px}
.trust-card h4{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--green);margin:0 0 6px;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif}
.trust-card p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.5}
@media(max-width:640px){.trust-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
@media(max-width:420px){.trust-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

/* ===== REPORT STEPS ===== */
.report-steps{margin:20px 0}
.report-step{display:grid;grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;gap:14px;padding:16px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);align-items:flex-start}
.report-step:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.report-step-num{width:42px;height:42px;background:var(--clay-ink);color:#fff;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Newsreader',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.report-step-body h4{margin:0 0 4px;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--dark)}
.report-step-body p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.6}
.report-step-body a{color:var(--green);font-weight:600;word-break:break-all}
.report-step-body a:hover{color:var(--clay)}

/* ===== SECTION SEAM DIVIDER ===== */
.cag-seam{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:26px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:.6rem 24px}
.cag-seam__line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.cag-seam img{height:30px;width:auto;display:block;opacity:.92;flex-shrink:0}
@media(max-width:600px){.cag-seam{gap:16px}.cag-seam img{height:24px}}

/* ===== FAQ ACCORDION (cag-faq-acc pattern) ===== */
.cag-faq-acc{margin:20px 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
.cag-faq-item{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(60,30,10,.05)}
