          <h2>The 5 Types of African Grey Parrot Scams You Need to Know</h2>

          <p>African Grey parrot fraud is not one-size-fits-all. Scammers use multiple tactics depending on the platform, the buyer, and how much they think they can extract. Here are the five most common fraud patterns to recognize before you send a single dollar.</p>

          <!-- Image: 5 Scam Types diagram -->
          <figure class="ig-panel" aria-label="The 5 Types of African Grey Parrot Scams">
            <div class="ig-head">
