          <h3 class="qa-label">How Long Does It Take to Verify a USDA AWA License Number?</h3>
          <div class="verify-steps" aria-label="USDA AWA verification steps">
            <div class="verify-step">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h4>Navigate to the USDA APHIS Public Search Tool</h4>
                <p>Go to <a href="https://www.aphis.usda.gov/awa/public-search" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aphis.usda.gov/awa/public-search</a> in any browser. This is the official federal database of all USDA AWA licensees — it is free, public, and updated regularly. No login required.</p>
              </div>
